href="#2-bold-colors-and-color-blocking">Bold colors and color blocking</a>.</li><li><a
href="#3-geometric-shapes">Geometric shapes</a>.</li><li><a
href="#4-vintage-or-retro-revival">Vintage or retro revival</a>.</li><li><a
